changelog:
Syberia OS v. 2.1 (17/12/18)

New: 
 - Full Substratum support (service)
 - Lockscreen clock&date font style and size 

Fixed:
 - Traffic monitor tint on dark QS
 - Use correct icon for ring volume
 - Fix the legacy color icons
 - Corrected padding of Syberia logo in statusbar.

Device side changes :
 - Added FM radio
 - Fixed Network issues
 - Fixed Display Glitch on pubg
 - Increased the number of status bar icons to 5
 - Moved Ambient Gestures to display settings
 - Added option to disable sim card


 Note - Make sure to do a clean flash ЁЯШГ
